name: Keys Group Holdings
overview: KEYS Group Holdings, LLC owns and operates behavioral health care centers through its subsidiaries. It offers trauma therapy, education, treatment, and juvenile rehabilitation; and psychiatric disorders, emotionally disturbed, and behaviorally disorder counseling services. KEYS Group Holdings, LLC also provides services such as operation and management of non-residential specialized education programs and day treatment centers in United States. Additionally, the company works in partnership with school boards, local, state, and federal agencies, physicians, judges, managed care providers, social workers, and parents to provide its services. KEYS Group Holdings, LLC was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Nashville, Tennessee. As of October 10, 2005, KEYS Group Holdings, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Universal Health Services Inc.
